@startuml
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

top to bottom direction

skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #666666
}

rectangle "Activation Events\ncommands, view, chat participant, LM tools" as Start #dae8fc
rectangle "Session Discovery\ngetWorkspaceStorageRoots\nfindSessionsForDays\nresolve titles" as Discover #dae8fc
rectangle "Source Selection\nparseCopilotSessionFile chooses\ndebug log, sibling chat session, or fallback" as Select #d5e8d4
rectangle "Normalization\nnormalizeEntry / normalizeParsedEntries\nparseEntries" as Normalize #d5e8d4
rectangle "Enrichment\nsubagent roll-up\nprompt composition\nspend summary" as Enrich #d5e8d4
rectangle "SessionGraph Projection\nserialize, tool usage, commands, risk flags" as Graph #d5e8d4
rectangle "Outputs\nTree view, quick pick, @usage, LM tools" as Output #fff2cc

Start --> Discover
Discover --> Select
Select --> Normalize
Normalize --> Enrich
Enrich --> Graph
Graph --> Output

note right of Select
Debug logs are preferred when
usable because they contain
billing, timing, and prompt metadata.
Chat sessions backfill transcript data.
end note

note right of Output
The same parsed session model drives
both the UI and the chat-facing tools.
end note
@enduml